gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 124, Nuggets 111
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Nuggets, 124-111. Jordan Clarkson recorded a team-high 27 points along with nine assists for the Jazz, with Lauri Markkanen (26 points, 12 rebounds) and Collin Sexton (22 points, four assists) combining for 48 points in the victory. Nikola Jokic tallied 27 points, 11 rebounds, and six assists for the Nuggets in the loss. The Jazz have won three in a row and improve to 19-20 in the regular season, while the Nuggets fall to 26-13.
